description: Phase 0 founder dataset v2 with stratified sentinels, timepoint charting (12h/24h/48h), and 48h dose-pair sentinels to detect biological convergence vs technical distortion.

control_design_rules.sentinel_spatial_stratification: Each sentinel type is distributed across quadrants; no adjacency runs are permitted by construction.
control_design_rules.late_timepoint_dose_pairs: At 48h, ER and mito sentinels are split into low/mid doses to quantify saturation via Q_s.
control_design_rules.timepoint_as_chart: Analyses must not mix timepoints; boundaries are chart-gated by timepoint health.

notes: Experimental (non-sentinel) assignments for 12h and 48h are inherited from the original Phase 0 design but randomized across plate positions to reduce spatial confounding.
24h experimental assignments mirror 12h to enable Goldilocks chart evaluation without introducing new compound coverage complexity.
